metadata.name: Mysterious Mountaintop Morning
metadata.description: A couple dressed in vibrant South American folk costumes defy gravity, their feet barely touching the ground, as they dance at breakneck speed on a majestic mountaintop. The rising sun casts a warm glow on their bodies, as the mysterious spotlight on them enchants the scene. Digital painting created by Yolantis with AI and digital post processing. 2048 x 2048 pixels, 1.7 MB JPG
